              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15192957420379873585">I don&apos;t care if the plot lines were far-fetched, it was a page turner for me until the end. Escapism reading, which is what I needed right now. Many characters and twists &amp; turns kept one guessing about who were the bad guys</span>
  <span id="freeText15192957420379873585" style="display:none">I don't care if the plot lines were far-fetched, it was a page turner for me until the end. Escapism reading, which is what I needed right now. Many characters and twists &amp; turns kept one guessing about who were the bad guys</span>
