  <span id="freeText9428375543383246044" style="display:none">Interesting story, wonder why I took so long to read it? Normally I can get through a Baldacci in 2 to 3 days at most. This story reminds me of Grisham's thrillers; The Pelican Brief and The Firm I think...<br /><br /><b>
